We Stand with the Caregiver Nation   Their story, our promise.  


 




 



      Providing technology, advocacy and insights that bring support and confidence to caregivers    


Providing technology, advocacy and insights that bring support and confidence to caregivers
Every day, tens of millions of caregivers provide dignity and comfort to a loved one in need of care. At Seniorlink, we are proud to stand alongside these silent heroes.
For over 15 years, Seniorlink has pioneered solutions for caregivers. We began with Caregiver Homes, our unique model of in-home care that dedicates experienced care teams to work alongside caregivers and their families, offering guidance and support while leveraging caregiver-informed technology. This innovative approach earned Caregiver Homes recognition as the first home and community-based organization to receive the National Committee for Quality Assurance's (NCQA) highest level of accreditation for Case Management.
Today, we continue to transform the caregiving experience with Vela. This powerful new technology platform facilitates coaching and collaboration between case managers, network providers, and family caregivers, with the goal of providing insight that leads to intervention – and measurable improvement in outcomes. 








 

 

 









Committed to those caring for a loved one at home
Our dedicated care teams make sure caregivers are never alone on their journey of caring for a loved one at home.
Learn More  







Where compassion meets technology
Our transformative technology will bring peace of mind to caregivers by allowing them to collaborate with coaches and care teams and access a broad network of helpful resources and information.
Learn More  




 



