ABOUT Seniorlink: Our Story and Our Team







Seniorlink is an innovator of care collaboration solutions that balance human touch and technology to deliver better outcomes, resulting in lower costs for providers and health systems. Built on more than a decade of care management expertise, our solutions deliver high-quality, person-centered care by pairing interdisciplinary care teams – including family caregivers – with our novel care collaboration platform, Vela. 
Our Story
Seniorlink was founded by E. Byron Hensley, Jr. in 2000. Impassioned by his own family’s caregiving experience, Byron sought to expand the resources available to family caregivers around the country.
In 2005 the company launched Caregiver Homes, a unique in-home care management solution that pairs experienced care teams with live-in caregivers and their families, offering coaching and support at every step. After launching in Massachusetts, Caregiver Homes expanded steadily and today serves thousands of families across six states. It was the first home and community-based service in the nation to receive the National Committee for Quality Assurance's (NCQA) highest level of Accreditation for Case Management, and is the only NCQA-approved provider for case management in all states where it operates today.
In 2016, Seniorlink launched a HIPAA-secure care collaboration platform, Vela, to address the full spectrum of care management needs. Vela is designed to allow all members of a patient's care team – including case managers, providers, and caregivers both inside and outside the home – to communicate seamlessly. In combining this technology with a proven model for case management, Seniorlink offers solutions to plan, deliver, and coordinate care efficiently for any patient population. 
Our commitment to caregivers remains strong as we continually seek new ways to honor and support the mission of more than 60 million caregivers nationwide.
Our Purpose
We are committed to continually pioneering solutions that bring together knowledge, human touch and innovation to transform the caregiving experience. At Seniorlink, we stand with the Caregiver Nation, honoring caregivers and their families and ensuring they will never be alone on their daily journey of providing compassionate care.




